{"tid":1892164,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"[2020 4月新番] 數碼暴龍01 重啟","createTime":"2020-02-22T10:48:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-23T08:47:41.000Z","uid":14503,"like":2,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"0ba6e7e8c3c9c03f6230581a8e6648be421ee252","tid":1892164,"uid":14503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T10:48:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n套大電影都未睇就收到呢個消息<br />\n但冇人討論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n《數碼暴龍大冒險最後的進化絆》將於 2 月 21 日在日本上映，如無意外，這本來應是太一最後的故事。沒想到近日官方宣布，《數碼暴龍》將會推出電視動畫新作，有消息指動畫名叫《數碼暴龍大冒險 &Psi;》，不過尚有待確定。<br />\n<br />\n根據現時的資料，動畫將於 2020 年 4月 每週日早上 9 點，富士電視台放送，監督為櫻田博之，劇本由富岡淳廣撰寫。故事時間設定於 2020 年東京，八神太一的年齡則是回到小學 5 年級，但完全是新故事，會有新設計的數碼機，登場人物亦有稍微改變，主體劇情同樣是數碼獸影響現實世界，主角等人須進入數碼世界化解危，意味就是類似 Reboot 的做法。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://resource01-proxy.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/2545000/2547728/EOkcw8eXsAA_6Gc_600.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01-proxy.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2545000%2F2547728%2FEOkcw8eXsAA_6Gc_600.jpg&h=c9881731&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://ezone.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/2547728\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fezone.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Farticle%2F2547728&d=l2jL6rfoxymyXK22uA%2BdgkBo7c%2BYFxEppcXi0rJe94o%3D&h=570d4464\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://ezone.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/2547728</a>"},{"pid":"0560ca84d8f76de739c2fc6ef80df2f889b9cd72","tid":1892164,"uid":324229,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"